// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1656 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 87d01d14-40d0-5e5e-b0d0-16fab383046f

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
